name: Remembrance, World #21
description:
-Days passed, he was lost, he knew this was another dream that has to pass but also knew all this shit had to be connected somehow.
He began searching for clues, trying to comprehend, building a sense of what is going on around him, so he wrote as he observed. -"This could all be gone before I know it."
As he was thinking all of this, the sound of a water drop falling was heard.
-"The mysterious girl is back!" the journal said. He began to draw all he could before she was gone again...|Check out the zoomed parts on IG, and feel free to contact me on socials for more in-depth content!
